Summer brides glow a little differently — not just from the warmth of the sun, but from the magic of perfectly balanced makeup that breathes with the season.

Think dewy skin kissed by golden light, soft coral tones, flushed cheeks, and eyes that sparkle like sunshine on water.
Every brushstroke is about enhancing her, not hiding — letting the skin breathe, letting the love shine.

Because summer isn’t just a season, it’s a feeling — and this bride wears it like a dream.

“There are places on this Earth that speak to your soul, and the Golden Temple is one of them. The sound of the shabads, the warmth of the people, and the stillness of the Sarovar—it all feels like a gentle reminder that peace is found within. Every prayer whispered here, every footstep taken barefoot, carries a sense of gratitude and devotion. I came here with a heart full of questions and left with a mind full of calm. Waheguru’s presence is felt in every moment spent here.”

Back to the place that feels less like a destination and more like a feeling.
It’s not just the views—it’s the peace, the memories, the version of me that only exists here.
Some places don’t need a filter… they just need a return ticket.
From the chaos to calm, this transition hits different every time.

latestPosts.caption:
“Watching my sister glow today hits different because I got to be the artist behind that glow! ✨ Creating this look was all about enhancing her natural beauty — soft glam eyes, radiant skin, and just the right pop of color to let her personality shine through.

But honestly, it wasn’t just about makeup. Sitting together, sharing laughs, reliving childhood memories, and turning this into a bonding moment reminded me why I love what I do. Makeup isn’t just art; it’s storytelling. And this story? It’s one of sisterhood, love, and making memories that last forever. ❤️
 
Thank you for trusting me with your face and your heart, sis. You’re my forever muse. 💫”
@yaanatherani 
.
.
#sistergoals #sisterlove❤️ #sisterwives #childhood

"All eyes may be on the bride, but her sister carries a special glow of pride and joy that’s just as radiant. 💕 Creating this elegant and timeless look was all about celebrating her role on this unforgettable day. Soft glam eyes, a flawless base, and a hint of blush to complement her natural beauty — a look that lasts through every emotion, every picture, and every celebration. Here’s to the sister who stood by the bride not just today but through every step of her journey.✨💍”
